WHERE: Hout Bay, Cape TownPRICE: R35mSituated in sought-after Riverside Terrace, this 1,600m contemporary home is set on a 2acre (8,850m ) river-front plot with magnificent mountain views. Features include two lounges, a study, chef s kitchen with a walk-in pantry, separate scullery and laundry as well as a linen room. The house has seven bedrooms, six with en-suite bathrooms, as well as a separate two-bedroom apartment.Agent: SeeffWHERE: Seapoint, Cape TownPRICE: R2.5m-R16mThe Signatura Group has just launched a sectional title development in Seapoint, about 200m from Queen s Beach opposite King s Road at the terminus of Regent Road. The Cosmopolitan will be a nine-storey building including 35 bachelor, one and two-bedroom units and three luxury penthouses with access to private roof terraces. The size of the units ranges from 42m to 187m .Agent: Signatura Group